<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@500;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<title>Biodata Kim Seon Ho</title>

<style>
body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #cde7f0, #eaf6fb);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    height: 100vh;
}


.bungkus {
    width: 950px;
    height: 520px;
    display: grid;
    
    background-color:maroon;
    
}


.left {
    position: relative;
    background: url('https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/the-dramas/images/c/ca/20.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20240523004230') center/cover;
}

.left::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.3), transparent);
}


.right {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
    padding: 40px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
}


.title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 34px;
    color: #2c3e50;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}


.line {
    width: 60px;
    height: 3px;
    background: #89c2d9;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}


.info {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: #333;
}


.desc {
    margin-top: 20px;
    padding: 15px;
    border-left: 4px solid #89c2d9;
    background: #eef6f8;
    transition: 0.3s;
}

.desc:hover {
    transform: translateX(6px);
}


.footer {
    margin-top: 20px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #555;
}


@keyframes fadeIn {
    from {opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px);}
    to {opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0);}
}


@media(max-width: 768px){
    .bungkus {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        height: auto;
    }
    .left {
        height: 300px;
    }
}
</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="bungkus">

    <div class="left"></div>

    <div class="right">
        <div class="title">Kim Seon Ho</div>
        <div class="line"></div>

        <div class="info">
            <strong>Nama:</strong> Kim Seon Ho <br>
            <strong>Umur:</strong> 40 tahun <br>
            <strong>Tempat, Tanggal Lahir:</strong> Seoul, 8 Mei 1986 <br>
            <strong>Drama:</strong> Start-Up, Hometown Cha-Cha-Cha, 100 Days My Prince, Catch The Ghost <br>
            <strong>Fans:</strong> Jutaan penggemar di seluruh dunia
        </div>

        <div class="desc">
            Kim Seon Ho merupakan aktor Korea Selatan yang dikenal melalui kemampuan aktingnya yang natural dan penuh emosi, serta mampu membangun karakter yang kuat dan berkesan di setiap perannya.
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            Saya mengidolakan Kim Seon Ho karena ia memiliki wajahyang menawan, badan atletis, serta kepribadian yang hangat dan baik hati. Pesonanya terasa sederhana namun tetap elegan dan menginspirasi banyak orang.
        </div>
    </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
